OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783696744
OL,3,CInspectors deem NHS Borders maternity
OL,4,Cunit 'compassionate' and 'respectful'
OL,6,FMaternity services within NHS Borders
OL,7,Fwere deemed 'compassionate' and
OL,8,F'respectful' following an unannounced
OL,9,Finspection.
OL,11,FHealth Improvement Scotland also found
OL,12,Fareas requiring improvement such as
OL,13,Fthe time taken to complete reviews
OL,14,Finto adverse events like baby loss -
OL,15,Fsometimes up to 18 months.
OL,17,FOne mum, Mhari, who gave birth to a
OL,18,Fbaby girl named Robyn at Borders
OL,19,FGeneral Hospital in Melrose this week,
OL,20,Fsaid the care she received was
OL,21,F"faultless."
OL,26,@}D@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783696744
OL,3,CInspectors deem NHS Borders maternity
OL,4,Cunit 'compassionate' and 'respectful'
OL,6,F"I've given birth in another health
OL,7,Fboard and the experience was awful,
OL,8,Fhere it was completely different," she
OL,9,Fexplained.
OL,11,F"The staff were amazing, from the
OL,12,Fmoment I came in it was so calm."
OL,14,FMhari was booked in for a caesarean
OL,15,Fsection but went into labour
OL,16,Fspontaneously the day before.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@bO]sD@AOUtD@aO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783696744
OL,3,CInspectors deem NHS Borders maternity
OL,4,Cunit 'compassionate' and 'respectful'
OL,6,F"Everyone kept me informed, I never
OL,7,Fhad to worry about what was happening
OL,8,Fnext. Each person who spoke to me from
OL,9,Fthe midwives to the anaesthetist were
OL,10,Fjust brilliant."
OL,12,FHealth Improvement Scotland (HIS)
OL,13,Fcarried out an unannounced inspection
OL,14,Fof the hospital's maternity services
OL,15,Fin March.
OL,17,FChief Inspector Donna Maclean said she
OL,18,Ffound the care given to patients to be
OL,19,F"compassionate, responsive, and
OL,20,Frespectful."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@PO]{D@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783696744
OL,3,CInspectors deem NHS Borders maternity
OL,4,Cunit 'compassionate' and 'respectful'
OL,6,F"During our inspection we observed
OL,7,Fcalm, person-centred care and staff
OL,8,Fworking together to maintain good
OL,9,Fcommunication and provide
OL,10,Fcompassionate, responsive and
OL,11,Frespectful care.
OL,13,F"The maternity unit was calm, tidy,
OL,14,Fclean and maintained to a high
OL,15,Fstandard. Women we spoke with were
OL,16,Fcomplimentary of the care received and
OL,17,Fwould recommend maternity services
OL,18,Fwithin Borders General Hospital to
OL,19,Ffamily and friends."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783696744
OL,3,CInspectors deem NHS Borders maternity
OL,4,Cunit 'compassionate' and 'respectful'
OL,6,FBut there were also 10 areas of
OL,7,Fimprovement identified.
OL,9,FThe report highlighted that reviews
OL,10,Finto still births and neonatal deaths
OL,11,Fwere taking up to 18 months to
OL,12,Fcomplete.
OL,14,FGuidance states that serious adverse
OL,15,Fevent reviews (SAERs) such as those
OL,16,Flooking into the death of a baby,
OL,17,Fshould be commissioned within 10
OL,18,Fworking days of the incident.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783696744
OL,3,CInspectors deem NHS Borders maternity
OL,4,Cunit 'compassionate' and 'respectful'
OL,6,FHIS found the time frame for
OL,7,Fcommissioning such a review in NHS
OL,8,FBorders ranged from one month to five
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,FThey also noted that SAER reviews were
OL,12,Fstill in progress 'up to 18 months
OL,13,Ffollowing a significant adverse event.'
OL,15,FThe "primary purpose" of such reviews
OL,16,Fis to provide bereaved parents with
OL,17,F"clear answers" about whether the care
OL,18,Fthey received was safe and
OL,19,Fappropriate, and if different care
OL,20,Fcould have resulted in a different
OL,21,Foutcome for them.
OL,26,@wD@EOUwD@UO]yD@AOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783696744
OL,3,CInspectors deem NHS Borders maternity
OL,4,Cunit 'compassionate' and 'respectful'
OL,6,FThe health watchdog said that such
OL,7,Fdelays can "impact significantly on
OL,8,Fthe mental health and grieving journey
OL,9,Fof the family involved" as well as
OL,10,Fhold up any improvements services.
OL,12,FSarah Horan, Director of Nursing and
OL,13,FMidwifery at NHS Borders said they
OL,14,Fwant to work with HIS to learn how
OL,15,Fthey can complete these reviews in a
OL,16,Ffaster way.
OL,26,@oD@LOUqD@WO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783696744
OL,3,CInspectors deem NHS Borders maternity
OL,4,Cunit 'compassionate' and 'respectful'
OL,6,F"It's really important when something
OL,7,Fgoes wrong in a pregnancy or a labour
OL,8,Fand delivery that we understand what
OL,9,Fwent wrong and we do everything we can
OL,10,Fto prevent that happening to someone
OL,11,Felse.
OL,13,F"Because we're a small service we
OL,14,Fdon't want to be 'marking our own
OL,15,Fhomework' so often we go to other
OL,16,Fhealth boards to assist us, so that we
OL,17,Fhave someone independent who can tell
OL,18,Fus what we can do better, and that has
OL,19,Fan implication on the time.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783696744
OL,3,CInspectors deem NHS Borders maternity
OL,4,Cunit 'compassionate' and 'respectful'
OL,6,F"We speak to the families straight
OL,7,Faway, we put any changes we need to in
OL,8,Fplace straight away, so it's not that
OL,9,Fwe wait 18 months for a full report to
OL,10,Fput changes in place.
OL,12,F"And even if the outcome of the review
OL,13,Fmight take time, the family do have a
OL,14,Fsingle point of contact within our
OL,15,Fservice throughout.
OL,17,F"We want to work with HIS to learn how
OL,18,Fwe can make this happen in a faster
OL,19,Fway but still making sure we have the
OL,20,Fquality of the report that the family
OL,21,Fneeds and deserves."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@TO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/10
